@host = http://localhost:3000

### ヘルスチェック
GET {{host}}/

### お問い合わせ（正常系）→ 200 { ok: true, data }
POST {{host}}/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "佐藤",
  "email": "s@example.com",
  "title": "件名",
  "message": "本文"
}

### お問い合わせ（異常系: 全項目不正）→ 400 { errors }
POST {{host}}/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "email": "bad",
  "title": "",
  "message": ""
}

### お問い合わせ（異常系: email のみ不正）→ 400 errors.fieldErrors.email
POST {{host}}/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "佐藤",
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "title": "件名",
  "message": "本文"
}

### お問い合わせ（異常系: 必須項目欠落）→ 400
POST {{host}}/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "佐藤",
  "email": "s@example.com"
}
